      "speaker": "Court finding"
    },
    {
      "evidence_id": "E002",
      "type": "LEGAL_FINDING",
      "text": "The defendants established, prima facie, that they were entitled to judgment as a matter of law dismissing the complaint insofar as asserted against them.",
